graph LR
    ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelController -->|extends functionality| KServe[KServe v0.13+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|creates Routes| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API v1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|template processing| OpenshiftTemplate[OpenShift Template API v1<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ODHModelController -.->|service mesh<br/>MESH_DISABLED=false| Istio[Istio/Maistra v2.5+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|auth enforcement| Authorino[Authorino v0.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|alternative auth| Kuadrant[Kuadrant AuthPolicy v1beta3<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA v2.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.13+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|NIM integration<br/>NIM_STATE| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|reads config| DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>ODH CRD]
    ODHModelController -->|reads init config| DSCInit[DSCInitialization<br/>ODH CRD]
    ODHModelController -.->|registers metadata<br/>MODELREGISTRY_STATE| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ODH Component]

    %% KServe Dependencies
    KServe -->|serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving v1.12+]
    KServe -->|uses for routing| Istio

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ODHModelController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| ODHModelController
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|deploy via SDK| ODHModelController

    %% Infrastructure Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    KServe -->|creates workloads| K8sAPI

    %% Runtime Dependencies (for inference workloads)
    subgraph "Serving Runtimes (Managed)"
        vLLM[vLLM<br/>CPU/CUDA/Gaudi/ROCm/Multinode]
        Caikit[Caikit<br/>Standalone/TGIS]
        OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server<br/>KServe/ModelMesh]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Detector]
    end

    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| vLLM
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| Caikit
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| OVMS
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| HuggingFace

    %% Styling
    style ODHModelController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    style KServe fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenshiftRoute fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenshiftTemplate fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style Istio fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Authorino fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Kuadrant fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style KEDA fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style NGC fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style DSC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSCInit fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style Dashboard fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333
    style Notebooks fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333

    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333

    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Caikit fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
